Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊～ 果然還是被罵了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟鬼沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一說要離家出走...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她居然說「辦得到妳請便～」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說被說成這樣了還能不走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳... 連這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個的話我睡不著！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這個毛巾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有有這個我也睡不著！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底準備了多少東西啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能離家出走多久啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說妳也不能都不去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 你也敢這樣說？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的學校啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要休息一次就會變得很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最初的一次很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是休息一天而已並不會有什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒什麼改變就這樣日復一日 日復一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣積累下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到察覺的時候自己已經完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒資格說這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊？ 也是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿海你真厲害 沒有白當家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿海果然沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在自己困難的時候 也總是為別人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳夠了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳總是這樣 只考慮別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話芽間才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和雪集談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直被芽間所束縛...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會不會不太好呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是這樣說 但她現在就在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 所以說 這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不相信芽間的事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不... 我不是說不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等～ 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買咖喱牛肉回來了喔～ 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五百二十元呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱牛肉撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來看日記的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的咖喱牛肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.89,TEAM,,0000,0000,0000,,傲嬌字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.89,STAFF,,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯 雨燕叶 時間 妖喵朔 後期 翡璃月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看過這個之後或許就能知道芽間的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 翻開了喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有著我所不瞭解的芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所不瞭解芽間的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(今天和大家一起去玩了 非常有趣)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(今天和大家一起去玩了 非常開心)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好隨意...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有趣就是開心 只有這些差別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不擅長作文呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 這個有些不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩的時候跌倒了 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！ 這裡也不一樣喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起去仁給太的媽媽探病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探病啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來以前經常去呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太的媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在住院呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了～ 我們寫信給神吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請神讓仁太的媽媽快點好起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家決定一起來做煙火 我想雖然很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把信裝在火箭煙火裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後發送給神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 願望會不會就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊～ 一定是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候本來想做的結果沒做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我的媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不良仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞蛋仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太什麼的才不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半夜吃飯會變成豬喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要變成豬的是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 鹽拉麵 加蛋花的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為找不到賢者拉麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳點吃的讓妳心情好一些...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸差不多要回來了 快點吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我明天也會去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說... 別跟著我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是獎勵 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不能再做奇怪的事喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你沒去學校還穿著校服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係啊！ 穿什麼都是時尚的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依據火藥類管理法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要使用煙火用的火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要十八歲以上 擁有國家資格才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是玩具煙火之類的話似乎還可以搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也需要有執照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 果然不行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想做煙火是要證照的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 昨天打掃的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜集大量的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把火藥全部倒出來集中在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把火藥包進廁紙芯裡 會燒起來所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不廢話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕 小鬼好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以前認為這是可行的呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前就算是這種東西 也覺得它一定能飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我們能做出比煙火大會看到的更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛得更高的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中生看起來已經完全是大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好像什麼都能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 總覺得什麼都能辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先找個可以實現的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是這樣說 應該沒希望的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們做再多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你說的芽間的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好跟你家的芽間確認過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向本人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我是害怕向她本人確認吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間感覺似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直走在前面的宿海以及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在背後望著他的可憐雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶？ 為什麼你不說出來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是他說要到秘密基地集合...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天... 好像是芽間提出來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是芽間打電話叫我們出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了...那天 她好像說有什麼事想商量...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易想起來了 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘記了一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間那天說要大家對宿海保密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有認識會做的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工地的一個大叔在祭典的時候是花火師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了仁太 想做煙火嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦... 啊... 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是想做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不... 和波波他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣阿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫你拜託他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太！ 仁太！ 仁太！ 仁太～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走不出孔多魯鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你連絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事下次再說吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算簡單的也是需要這麼多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要做都還是能做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂... 我都沒見過那樣的金額
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係！ 一定能湊齊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和安鳴拼命打工的話 吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你... 你能不能不要擅自做主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好嘛！ 互相幫助嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦 只要安鳴一週七天都打工就沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？ 我都還沒同意呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也... 要做...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要做！ 打工！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡輸入金額就對了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是中古品的價格 然後這邊是新品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 然後在這裡輸入差額吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我花了一個月才掌握的技巧你一來就會了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳花太久了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個你就完全不行了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧！ 果然是傳說中的那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工倒沒請假啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校就沒去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看那邊 不就是不來學校的那小子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 這兩個傢伙有一腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～ 真好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎～ 光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎... 怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟小時候一樣沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿膠帶 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿... 海...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著喔！ 安鳴～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NICE CATCH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿海在打工啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙火的事 看來是認真的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也湊點錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給宿海去胡鬧嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不參加的話 我也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶！ 出來走走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去喝杯茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快考試了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年級第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年級第二居然說這種話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪著你可是相當累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 這麼晚... 不良！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太絕對怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上馬上就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上馬上就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是狗狗的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狗是母的 仁太一定在做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做的真好呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫歐斯卡爾 雌性 七歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴哥好可愛 褶折真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐斯卡爾是奈奈氏的招牌狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是母的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小客人打著招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托歐斯卡爾的福 客人增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老奶奶也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐斯卡爾今天也有精神的笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那請在這名簿上簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了... 仁太退學了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 為什麼這樣問呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 問這種奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 前幾天 看到他好像在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 都把這些事都告訴爸爸了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們家是採自由主義的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些事都是仁太自己做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關係！ 有關係有關係有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關係～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 今天沒有我的班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說店長好像很欣賞他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上和他一起的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羊山的工地？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會不會太累了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要賺錢還是體力勞動最快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火箭煙火 錢也都要飛走了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙火...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多為自己的事情考慮一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓... 讓人不爽啊！ 妳那種態度！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 嗯... 是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 雪集他們最近有聯絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 偶爾有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們也來多好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼在意仁太的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？ 仁太就是仁太嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一直叫仁太的嗎？ 是會怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人～ 這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄完了來這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子好拚命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！ 很帥呢！ 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間... 沒有在為自己著想的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太一直都在為芽間著想啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 當心腳下喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自改變燈的方向啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是風吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風能吹得動燈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很帥呢！ 閃閃發光的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很帥呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼吃得完啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽做的味道很接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶！ 仁太 學校辛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 比一直待在家裡要輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有種活著的真實感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是說那個活著...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間看到有活著的真實感的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也感覺到活著了喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我把定金先拿來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能還差很多 不過這樣可以先開始做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛... 不好意思 但這可能沒辦法了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心跟祭典的幹事說溜嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後他就生氣罵我居然幫高中生做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼拼命地賺錢呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？ 那個幹事 我直接去找他談
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個... 本間家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽間家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他們好像在為妳做各種努力喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是胡來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是超和平Busters喔！
